title: Global Capitalism: October 2015 Monthly Economic Update-Richard
description:
Global Capitalism: October 2015 Monthly Economic Update-Richard D Wolff

Co-sponsored by Democracy at Work, Left Forum, and Judson Memorial Church

These programs begin with 30 minutes of short updates on important economic events of the last month. Then Wolff analyzes several major economic issues. For October these will include:

1. Volkswagen: Scandal for Capitalism, Germany and Beyond

2. Bad US Job Numbers; Wages Stagnate; Prices Fallâ€¦.Downturn Looms

3. Trans-Pacific Partnership (TPP): Corps/Govts Do Their Trade Deals
